---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import ownerImage from '../assets/owner.jpg';
import { firm } from '../data/site';
---

<section class="section">
	<div class="shell spotlight-grid">
		<div class="portrait-card">
			<div class="portrait-frame">
				<Image
					src={ownerImage}
					alt="Tracy A. Cinocca"
					widths={[360, 520, 720]}
					sizes="(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 34vw"
					loading="lazy"
					format="avif"
				/>
			</div>
			<div class="portrait-caption">
				<strong>Tracy A. Cinocca, J.D.</strong>
				<span>{firm.serviceArea}</span>
				<span>{firm.fullAddress}</span>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="band">
			<p class="eyebrow">Meet Tracy</p>
			<h2 class="section-title">Attorney-led review from a Tulsa office serving Oklahoma clients.</h2>
			<p class="lead">
				Most people reach out because they need an honest first read on an injury matter,
				planning documents that need attention, or a sensible legal next step before time and money
				go to waste.
			</p>
			<ul class="checklist">
				<li>Tulsa office serving Tulsa, Bixby, Broken Arrow, and nearby Oklahoma communities</li>
				<li>Attorney-led review instead of a generic intake handoff</li>
				<li>Clear next-step guidance on injury, planning, family, and business matters</li>
				<li>1,500+ satisfied clients and a 98% successful case rate</li>
			</ul>
			<div class="quote" style="margin-top: 18px;">
				Most people do not want a speech. They want to know whether the matter fits, what needs
				attention first, and what should happen next.
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
